{"tid":1220249,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 海底隧道收費站免費通車?","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:32:47.000Z","uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33a3587e0f726a87fa7fa81d5fc38b258d532a58","tid":1220249,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如<span style=\"color: red;\">堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽講 週末海底隧道收費廣場有Pok&eacute;mon 捉 <br />\n大家千其唔好去</span></span>"},{"pid":"f693fa8a8d8b26e243bf637d9c9df3b312489036","tid":1220249,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84988e59421549006409e3c85abc6c8979b8669c","tid":1220249,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}